ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities

类 SourceCodeChange

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities.SourceCodeChange
  • 直接已知子类:
    Delete, Insert, Move, Update

    public class SourceCodeChange
extends Object
    General (abstract) representation of a source code change.

    Each source code change has a

    • StructureEntityVersion rootEntity that describes in which attribute, class, or method the changes was made. The rootEntity is taken from the right AST, i.e., new version of the StructureEntityVersion.
    • SourceCodeEntity changedEntity that describes which source code entity has changed. In case of
      • Delete: the entity that was deleted; it is taken from the left AST, i.e., old version.
      • Insert: the entity that was inserted; it is taken from the right AST, i.e., new version.
      • Move: the entity that was moved; it is taken from the left AST, i.e., old version.
      • Update: the entity that was updated; it is taken from the left AST, i.e., old version.
    Other entities involved in a source code change are described in the corresponding concrete implementation.
    作者:
    Beat Fluri, Giacomo Ghezzi, zubi
    另请参阅:
    Delete, Insert, Move, Update
